{"tid":194454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民主進步黨原來已經解散","createTime":"2017-04-10T03:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T04:37:15.000Z","uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1796703f0920554b2790feafea1a47aeefcc7325","tid":194454,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:30:54.000Z","msg":"2017年3月4日，該黨宣布由於沒有有足夠的會員人數召開年度會員大會，即日起停止運作。<br />\n2017年3月26日，該黨宣布為免「民主進步黨」名義被濫用而對其他華文地區的同名政團受到不必要影響，正式聲明解散，其Facebook專頁專頁亦將於十四日後刪除。<br />\n楊繼昌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68de8ea08b6906c47b6d010afedb83e4774df521","tid":194454,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3951a7fb3f1561b131d4d19d58f6b2f6316c9795","tid":194454,"uid":64225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:33:14.000Z","msg":"昌昌都係多鳩餘"},{"pid":"8d96bbc6d1cfd49dda57e1f75282ebed0cbbc955","tid":194454,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:13:30.000Z","msg":"佢為香港民主努力，不論付出多少，大家都應該支持，自己人都唔支持自己人爭取民主，成日踩低別人，對於爭取民主沒有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n希望佢繼續為香港民主努力。<br />\n<br />\n申利：對佢冇認識。"},{"pid":"aae7b070677a2d21ee7c4426cdec86ec4dc98fd0","tid":194454,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"講好有健身教練出黎阻止示威者用暴力呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee7446a29d3f87772f45df894dcd2bd0e401723","tid":194454,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:36:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7291fcbf80df61628ba383c1732974cf77699a6","tid":194454,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20